~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : unignore                                  ~FTRNUTS Version 3.0.2
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : unignore <username>

   This command allows you to turn off ignoring on a specific user, 
   allowing all tells and shouts from that user again.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : ignore, showignore, ignall, igntell, ignshout
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
